document.discussion_title: Vehicle fire closes part of Research Blvd. frontage road in NW Austin
document.topic_text: Vehicle fire closes part of Research Blvd. frontage road in NW Austin American-Statesman Monday 25th April, 2016 A vehicle fire has forced authorities to shut down one lane on the northbound frontage road of Research Boulevard near West Braker Lane in Northwest Austin.At 2:30 p.m., the Austin Fire Department received reports of a vehicle on fire at 10401 Research Blvd. No one was inside the car, and no injuries were reported.Firefighters have put out the flames but said drivers can still expect delays in the area because of road closures....
